    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v1 + 0.43) / (tmp + 0.48 * v1 + 0.00)))
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.31) * v1) - wp.exp(v2))
    v1 = wp.sin((v1 + wp.sin(v1 + 0.26)))
    tmp = wp.abs(v2)
    v2 = wp.cos((tmp * tmp))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.58)) / tmp)
    v0 = v0
